<Paragraph>
Essential XlsIO is a library that is used to create Excel workbooks without being dependent on Microsoft Excel.
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph>
This category contains the samples that demonstrate the creation of macro file and editing the macro in an existing Excel template. Here is a list of samples with description.
</Paragraph>

<List>
<ListItem><Paragraph><Bold>Create Macro</Bold> - This sample demonstrates how to create a macro file in Excel from code.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph><Bold>Edit Macro</Bold> - This sample demonstrates XlsIO's capability of editing a macro in an existing template and saving the file in XLS, XLSM and XLTM formats.</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>
